Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Tehran hostage crisis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040h3xn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Nov 1979
President Carter's standing as statesman rises after response to Tehran hostage crisis. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less